    <item>
      <title>中国捍卫5%的增长目标，暗示流动性增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/china-defends-5-target-vows-vigorous-effort-to-grow-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国最高经济官员为今年经济增长约 5% 的计划进行了辩护，并暗示可能会增加流动性。一天前，一些经济学家因认为缺乏足够的政策支持而对这一雄心勃勃的目标表示怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/china-defends-5-target-vows-vigorous-effort-to-grow-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 07:19:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度加强打击影子银行，JM Financial 暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/india-bars-jm-financial-from-lending-against-shares-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度央行禁止 JM Financial Ltd. 子公司发放股票和债券贷款，加上最近采取的抑制投机性投资的监管举措，导致 JM Financial Ltd. 在孟买股价暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/india-bars-jm-financial-from-lending-against-shares-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 14:29:00 GMT</pubDate>
